### =================================================
### TEST SOAP API ENDPOINTS
### =================================================

### Test 4: Get Menu (SOAP Request)
POST {{soapBaseUrl}}/soap
Content-Type: text/xml
SOAPAction: "getMenu"

<soap:Envelope xmlns:soap="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/envelope/">
   <soap:Body>
      <getMenuRequest/>
   </soap:Body>
</soap:Envelope>

### Test 5: Place Order (SOAP Request)
POST {{soapBaseUrl}}/soap
Content-Type: text/xml
SOAPAction: "placeOrder"

<soap:Envelope xmlns:soap="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/envelope/">
   <soap:Body>
      <placeOrderRequest>
         <customerName>Alice Johnson</customerName>
         <itemId>1</itemId>
         <quantity>3</quantity>
      </placeOrderRequest>
   </soap:Body>
</soap:Envelope>

### Test 6: Calculate Total (SOAP Request)
POST {{soapBaseUrl}}/soap
Content-Type: text/xml
SOAPAction: "calculateTotal"

<soap:Envelope xmlns:soap="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/envelope/">
   <soap:Body>
      <calculateTotalRequest>
         <itemId>2</itemId>
         <quantity>4</quantity>
      </calculateTotalRequest>
   </soap:Body>
</soap:Envelope>

### Test 7: Check Order Status (SOAP Request)
POST {{soapBaseUrl}}/soap
Content-Type: text/xml
SOAPAction: "checkOrderStatus"

<soap:Envelope xmlns:soap="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/envelope/">
   <soap:Body>
      <checkOrderStatusRequest>
         <orderId>1001</orderId>
      </checkOrderStatusRequest>
   </soap:Body>
</soap:Envelope>